The paper discusses uncertainty estimation in machine learning systems, specifically in the context of vision and image sequence prediction. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). However, since the focus is on image sequence prediction, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, and cs.CL.
